Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.48,1:29:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have so much to be thankful for.\NIt's hard to stand up.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.56,1:30:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the strength is\NI do already.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.15,1:30:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I'll do it verbally.\NI bless all of us here in the name of
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.00,1:30:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Almighty God now and forever. Amen.\NAnd that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.56,1:30:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to be careful not to fall over.\NThank you so much. It was truly a
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.40,1:31:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,wondrous day. Truly a wondrous day.\NTruly a wondrous day. And uh
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.63,1:31:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I I dedicate myself to you and and you\Nare God's gift to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.23,1:31:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So we all win. Amen.\NSuch a wonderful group. I I am
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.76,1:31:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,wonderful.\NLook at the beauty of these flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.67,1:31:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they unbelievable? Look at that.\NSo glad to see you all today. God bless
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.71,1:32:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you. God bless you all indeed.\NSo,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:04.96,1:32:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,>> thank you all.\NAll right, we have to get out of here by
Dialogue: 0,1:32:12.96,1:32:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,a certain time\Notherwise we get turned into mice.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.12,1:32:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, George. Yes.\NIt's such a incredible group, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.80,1:32:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Wow.\NUnbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.52,1:33:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\Nmen are not supposed to cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.08,1:33:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Thank you so much again. Is\Nthis working? I think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.48,1:33:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhoh.\NTake it away.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.04,1:33:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,>> I can't help but own the child in\Nmyself. You know,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.40,1:33:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to train him to be more\Nrespectful, but
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.60,1:33:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,he's hopeless.\NThe adult in me speaks to him,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.40,1:34:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"Child,\Nbehave."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.56,1:34:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says, "I am.\NI'm behaving like a child."
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.40,1:34:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Perfect fulfillment of\Nchildishness is to be childish, is it
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.84,1:34:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,not?\NYeah, we own the child.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.48,1:34:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We own the parent.\NWe own the adult.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.40,1:34:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All those aspects of ourel.\NSo we learn to be kind to the child in
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.60,1:34:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,ourself.\NWe learn to be child to love the child
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.76,1:35:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,in ourself.\NThe child is the divine child,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.67,1:37:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the Christ child within all of us.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.88,1:37:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fulfillment of the feeling of\Nallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.19,1:37:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank you so much for your gift. Thank\Nyou so much for your love.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.71,1:37:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your love is forever.\NYour love is forever. Nothing is lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.04,1:37:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Every hair on your head is counted. Your\Nlove is counted forever. And I thank
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.40,1:40:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you.\NI rever it. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.96,1:40:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We experience the joy of that which we\Nare.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.11,1:41:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And other people don't even guess who\Nthey are.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.08,1:41:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This the joy of our existence\Nof being with each other is
Dialogue: 0,1:41:06.32,1:41:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,overwhelming.\NIf I don't resist it, I will fall on the
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.63,1:41:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,floor.\NExquisite beyond all time.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.28,1:41:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment is forever.\NBeyond time. Forever.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.40,1:41:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Every hair on a head is gone.\NIncluding this moment.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.15,1:42:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This moment is forever.\NThat's pretty good for an afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.19,1:42:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They want us out of here by a certain\Ntime. So, we have to take take charge.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.88,1:42:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a dis that that's the\Ndisadvantage of having a physical body.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.36,1:42:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The sooner we get rid of it, the better,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.80,1:42:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can kick us out of any place.\NGod bless.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.76,1:43:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.19,1:43:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelujah.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.71,1:44:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelujah.\NHallelu
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.23,1:44:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hallelu.\NUh yes, this is Clifford. Well, uh we
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.28,1:44:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,used to have uh Thanksgiving\NAnd know Halloween, we had parties for
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.48,1:44:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,children and we'd have 30 uh kids plus\Ntheir parents and uh so it was sort of a
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.88,1:44:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,gayla event and we would have uh you\Nknow games and things like that. So we
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.08,1:45:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,began to decorate the place with the\Nscarecrows around uh so just to
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.80,1:45:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,celebrate the event and then we sort of\Ngot into the fun of it. So I started
Dialogue: 0,1:45:08.00,1:45:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,making scarecrows one time. And they're\Nthey're all articulated, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:11.19,1:45:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,everything works on them. And uh I had\Nabout a dozen made. I had daddy, mama,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:17.36,1:45:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and child, you know, and I had them on\Ndisplay at um local um
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.96,1:45:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,uh what do you call it? Greenhouse. Uh\NI forget what you call call it where you
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.00,1:45:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,sell plants and stuff.\N>> Nursery. Yes. So I had them on display
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.48,1:45:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,there and had them for sale. Yeah. So\Nthe nursery had a big display on them
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.71,1:45:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and homemade scarecrows.\NHalloween decor. Yeah. Yeah.
